msgstr "Ulac ableɣ usgrew arqaqan LVM s tazaẓlut '%s'"

#. TRANSLATORS: %s is the replaced by a device alias (e.g., "md1").
#: service/lib/agama/storage/config_checkers/md_raid.rb:98
#, c-format
